  "description": {
    "zh": "嘿，我这有个不错的提议。\n\n还记得之前那个自动霰弹枪的事儿吧？听说有个枪匠把Saiga-12半自动霰弹枪改成了全自动的，简直疯了！\n\n要是咱能搞到这种武器的稳定渠道，说不定你也能用上这些野兽级别的家伙。相信我，你可不想站在那枪口对面。\n\n行了，言归正传。你得弄点材料过来。几把普通的Saiga-12，还有一些全自动的AKM步枪，别拿半自动的糊弄我。再带点武器零件和工具，明白了吗？别带那些破烂回来。",
    "en": "Hey there! I got an exquisite offer for you.\n\nYou still remember the job from recently, do you? The one about the auto assault shotguns. Some gunsmith managed to modify semi automatic saiga 12 shotguns to be capable of fully automatic firing, how crazy is that!\n\nI could establish some connection and maybe you will get access to these weapons yourself? You should really see these beasts in action - wouldn't want to stand at the receiving end of that barrel, trust me.\nAnyway, enough talk. You gotta bring some supplies, a few of these ordinary saiga shotguns obviously, aswell as some AKM rifles. Make sure the AKs are fully automatic.\nDon't forget some weapon parts, and a few tools to work with, copy? Avoid bringing broken stuff."
  },
